oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Dean, Roxie; Baker, Bonnie, 1917-1990; O'Neal, Jamie; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and green on white) announcing Tin Pan South featuring Roxie Dean, Amy Dalley, Robin Lee Bruce, Bonnie Bake and special guest Jamie O'Neal at Douglas Corner in Nashville, Tennessee on April 4. Poster features a metal photoplate of a mouth.
